    "description": "<p>PolyAquol™-VO4 is an innovative, patented technology that redefines emulsions by creating a true Water-and-Oil Fusion (W+O). This 100% natural, Cosmos-certified, palm-free emulsifier, derived from polyglyceryl and oleic acid derivatives, performs exceptionally well even with 100% vegetable oils. PolyAquol™-VO4 enables the creation of cold-process emulsions with up to 80% internal water phase, providing unmatched control over viscosity. At low concentrations, it ensures stable, high-performance emulsions with luxurious sensory properties, surpassing competitors in both robustness and sensory experience, making it the perfect choice for innovative and sustainable cosmetic formulations. </p>",
